ol over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:imageForAnnotation:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:imageforannotation:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:imageForAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","title":"mapView:imageForAnnotation:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns an annotation image object to mark the given point annotation object on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map."}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:imageForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:imageForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}